body:
There are six Infinity Stones and six original Avengers.
What if Carol’s role will be to deliver the stones to each Avenger? She’s not gonna save they day for them, she’s just gonna give them a push.

summary:
Okay so I just thought of something...
In Winter Soldier, Zola said Nat was born in 1984 so if the MCU sticks to that she’d be...
body:
Okay so I just thought of something…

In Winter Soldier, Zola said Nat was born in 1984 so if the MCU sticks to that she’d be about seven or eight during the events of Captain Marvel. What if in the Captain Marvel movie post credits scene we see Director Peggy Carter walk into Fury’s office and they’re talking about Carol, and Fury calls Carol a hero. Peggy agrees with a small smile, but then hands him the file for his next assignment and says “Not all little girls turn out like her.” Fury opens it and we see a familiar red and black symbol. The scene cuts to a little red haired girl lying in bed looking out the window at the sky, her wrist chained to the bedpost like all the other little girls in the room.
